quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  6,125,"Kala mo Alla Faandii fewnude, O Ya√±√±iray …ìernde makko nden ja…ìugol Lislaamu. Kala kadi mo O Faandii Majjinnde, O Wa…óay …ìenrde makko faa…óunde fii ja…ìungol goonga ; o salora ja…ìugol goonga kan wano o ronkirta ≈ãabbagol yaha ka kammu. Ko wano non Alla Wa…óirta lepte …óen e hoore …ìen …ìe gom…óintaa."
  6,126,"Ko kaa diina …óoo woni ko Men Su…ìani maa an Nulaa…óo, ko laawol Alla foccii ngol. Gom…óii Men ∆Åannginii Aayeeje …óen, yim…ìe waajitotoo…ìe …ìen."
  6,127,"Hino woodani …ìe galle …óe …ìe hisata e majje kala bone -…óen woni Aljanna- Ko Alla woni Gi…óo ma…ì…ìe Walloowo …ìe ; sabu kon ko …ìe laatinoo hi…ìe golla e mo∆¥∆¥ereeji."
  6,128,"Janto an Nulaa…óo, √ëalnde Alla Moo…ìindiroyta yoora-ko'e …ìen ka yim…ìe e ka jinna, refti O Daala : "Ko onon yo dental Jinna, gom…óii on …óu…ó…óinorii majjingol yim…ìe …ìen sakkoo…ìe e laawol Alla ngol". Yim…ìe jokkunoo…ìe …ói …ìen jaaboo Joomi ma…ì…ìe : "Joomi amen, yoga e amen dakmitorii yoga : jinna dakmitorii ne…ó…óo, ne…ó…óo on kadi dakmitorii jinna haa men yottike ngal caatal ngal saatinan…óaa men √ëalnde Darngal". Alla Daala : "Ko Yiite ngen wonu √±ii…ìirde mon, ko on luttintii…ìe ton, si wanaa kon ko Alla Muuyi e emmbere dumunna hakkunde immineede …ìe ka genaale haa nde …ìe fokkitinoyee Jahannama ; ko …óum …óon woni ko Alla Ittintini e luttugol ma…ì…ìe ngol ka Yiite". Pellet, Joomi maa…óa an Nulaa…óo, ko √ëee√±u…óo e e…ì…ìoore mun e toppitagol mun, Anndu…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen hanndu…óo e ma…ì…ìe e lepte …óen."
  6,129,"Ko wano Men Wurtinoo jinnaaji …óin non e yim…ìe goo fii no …ói majjinira …ìe, Men Wurtirta kala too√±u…óo wo…ó…óitii e mo∆¥∆¥ere ; njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ko …ìe faggitotonoo kon e geddi."
  6,130,"Men Wi'anoya …ìe √ëalnde Darngal : "Ko onon yo dental jinna e yim…ìe, e araali on Nulaa…ìe jeyaa…ìe e mo'on, …ìe no janngana on ko Alla Jippini e ma…ì…ìe kon, …ìe rentina on hawrugol e ndee √ëalaande mo'on Darngal …óoo?" ∆Åe wi'a : "Ko non woniri, men qirritike hannde e hoore ko'e amen wonnde Nulaa…ìe Maa …ìen yottinno e amen, kono men fenni …ìe, men fenni kadi ndee …óoo √ëalaande". Nguurndam aduna …óam hodiri …ìe cu…óaari e neemaaji lannooji ; …ìe qirritii e hoore ko'e ma…ì…ìe wonnde …ìe laatino yeddu…ìe Alla e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen ka aduna. Ngol qirritagol non nafoytaa …ìe nden √ëalnde ; tawde laawike."
  6,131,"Ngon nganto Nulugol Nulaa…ìe e yim…ìe e jinna, ko fii wata gooto leptire bone, tawa non noddaandu Nulaa…óo yottaaki mo. Men Leptaali mofte si wanaa …ìaawo nde Men Immini Nulaa…óo e ma…ì…ìe."